snippet.textDisplay:
Main even was a shit show. I thought Romero was waiting to turn into an earthquake, so I waited 1st round, I waited 2nd round, I waited 3rd round, I waited 4th round, and I even waited until last 45 seconds of 5th round. Once I realized Romero was not giving a fuck, I said fuck it, put a fork in it, it's done.
What Israel had on his face when ref held his arm, exactly how I felt. I just threw my hands up and said "What a fuck was that, what-a-fuck-was-that?"

People that are ragging on Israel are kind of silly. Israel fought good, and he did what he had to. He is not a KO artist, he chopped Romero down.
